### List suppliers
GET http://localhost:3000/supplierMaster?page=1&pageSize=20&search=a&status=ACTIVE

### Lookup (dropdown)
GET http://localhost:3000/supplierMaster/lookup?search=a&limit=10

### Add supplier
POST http://localhost:4200/supplierMaster/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "supplierCode": "SUP-001",
  "supplierName": "Supplier A",
  "status": "ACTIVE",
  "email": "info123@gmail.com",
  "phone": "+0123456789",
  "paymentTermDays": 30,
  "tags": ["cosmetic"],
  "contacts": [{ "name": "Anh A", "phone": "+0123456788", "isPrimary": true }],
  "addresses": [{ "type": "OFFICE", "city": "HCM", "street": "123 LTK" }]
}

### Get detail
GET http://localhost:3000/supplierMaster/<id>

### Edit supplier
PUT http://localhost:3000/supplierMaster/edit/<id>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "supplierName": "Supplier A updated",
  "status": "INACTIVE",
  "ifMatchVersion": 1
}

### Contacts
GET http://localhost:3000/supplierMaster/<id>/contacts
POST http://localhost:3000/supplierMaster/<id>/contacts/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "New contact",
  "email": "contact@a.com",
  "isPrimary": true
}

### Addresses
GET http://localhost:3000/supplierMaster/<id>/addresses
POST http://localhost:3000/supplierMaster/<id>/addresses/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "BILLING",
  "city": "HCM",
  "street": "456 ABC",
  "isDefault": true
}
